belongs_to_collection.name: Mrs. Brown's Boys: The Original Series

original_title: Mrs. Brown's Boys: The Last Wedding - Part 2
overview: Part 2 of the story based on the hugely successful stage play. Join Agnes Brown and her doting family again as she tries to figure out... Who is marrying who? What is she going to wear? Will Simon get his promotion? And what is Rory doing with that man in his mouth?  Once again Write/Directory and Star Brendan O'Carroll takes us on a hilarious whirlwind tour of his "average" family.
title: Mrs. Brown's Boys: The Last Wedding - Part 2
